---
const skillCategories = [
  {
    label: 'NLP & LLMs',
    skills: ['Transformer Models', 'LLM Fine-tuning', 'RAG Systems', 'NLP'],
  },
  {
    label: 'Computer Vision',
    skills: ['Person Re-Identification', 'Pose Estimation', 'Edge Deployment'],
  },
  {
    label: 'ML Engineering',
    skills: ['MLOps', 'Model Deployment', 'API Integration', 'Data Science'],
  },
  {
    label: 'Research',
    skills: ['Bioinformatics', 'Information Retrieval', 'Reinforcement Learning'],
  },
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-24">
  <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <div
      class="border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.04] rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-all duration-300"
    >
      <p class="text-slate-400 leading-[1.9] mb-10" style="font-size: 1.05rem;">
        I'm a Vietnamese AI engineer based in Brisbane, Australia. After 3+ years building
        production AI systems at FPT Software and Viettel Post in Vietnam, building everything from
        MLOps platforms deployed on Samsung factory floors to NLP pipelines processing millions of
        customer calls. I moved to Australia to pursue a Master of AI at QUT and push deeper into research. I'm
        currently an AI Researcher at Cognilaw, a Research Assistant at QUT, and lead community
        roles at two university tech clubs. I care about AI that actually ships and solves real
        problems.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {
          skillCategories.map((cat) => (
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-cyan-400 tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-3">
                {cat.label}
              </h4>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                {cat.skills.map((skill) => (
                  <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/[0.08] text-slate-400 border border-indigo-500/20 hover:text-slate-200 hover:bg-indigo-500/15 transition-all duration-200 cursor-default">
                    {skill}
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
